@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Ready
GET {{baseUrl}}/ready

### Models
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/models

### Speech (success path requires valid env voice map + existing ref audio path)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/audio/speech
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "Qwen/Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-0.6B-Base",
  "provider": "qwen",
  "input": "Ciao, questo è un test di sintesi vocale.",
  "voice": "alloy",
  "response_format": "wav"
}

### Speech via Voxtral provider (requires local mlx-audio setup and allowed model)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/audio/speech
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "voxtral/mini-tts",
  "provider": "voxtral",
  "input": "Hello, this is a Voxtral test.",
  "voice": "alloy",
  "response_format": "wav"
}

